    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "~You can drop \"page\" parameter from urlSync, and use hitsPerPage (&hPP=) parameter instead, increasing it by initial hitsPerPage number.~\r\n\r\n~`var hitsPerPage = 12;`~\r\n\r\n~`$('body').on('click', '.ais-infinite-hits--showmore', function () {`~\r\n    ~`hitsPerPage += 12;`~\r\n    ~`search.helper.setQueryParameter('hitsPerPage', hitsPerPage);`~\r\n~`});`~\r\n\r\nDoesn't really work this way.",
